---
title: Pineapple-Apricot Chicken Breasts with Rosemary-Parmesan Potatoes and Snap Peas
description: Fresh pineapple and apricot spread make for the perfect sweet and savoury sauce to go with chicken breast! A side of potatoes is finished with rosemary and a sprinkle of Parmesan for maximum flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poitrines-de-poulet-a-la-sauce-ananas-abricots-bafd7bfe.jpg
